## Description {#details}

Provides unsafe access to ownership operations on <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/orc/symbolstringptr">SymbolStringPtr</a>.

This class can be used to manage <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/orc/symbolstringptr">SymbolStringPtr</a> instances from C.
